                      label.input-container__floating-label Name
                      input(type="text" name="name" placeholder="" autocomplete="off")
                    .input-container(js-input-focus)
                      label.input-container__floating-label Phone
                      input(type="text" name="phone" placeholder="" autocomplete="off")
                    .input-container(js-input-focus)
                      label.input-container__floating-label Email
                      input(type="text" name="email" placeholder="" autocomplete="off")
                    //- .input-container(js-input-focus)
                    //-   label.input-container__floating-label LINK TO PORTFOLIO OR DOWNLOAD THE FILE
                    //-   input(type="file" placeholder="" autocomplete="off")
                    .input-container.input-container--textarea(js-input-focus)
                      span
                      span
                      label.input-container__floating-label Message
                      textarea(name="message" rows="3" data-limit-rows="true" autocomplete="off")
                  .contacts__success
                    input.btn(type="submit" value="send")
                    p Thank you. Your request has been received and we will get back to you shortly.
                      br
                      | You are amazing!

            .vacancies__right
              .vacancies__right-about
                .vacancies__right-item
                  p.vacancies__right-title The duties of the employee include
                  p.vacancies__right-info • interaction with the art director and the development of the concept of design on digital media;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • development of design layouts for landing pages and banners, creating key visuals;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • responsibility for the design systems of the main customers;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • participation in the preparation of promotional sites and landing pages.
                .vacancies__right-item
                  p.vacancies__right-title The specialist must be
                  p.vacancies__right-info • concentrated;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • able to handle with routine work;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • knowing the basic concepts of graphics processing in Adobe (Photoshop and Illustrator).
                .vacancies__right-item
                  p.vacancies__right-title Preference is given to who
                  p.vacancies__right-info • can form design concepts;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • can create simple animations in AE.
                .vacancies__right-item
                  p.vacancies__right-title Conditions:
                  p.vacancies__right-info • cooperation in the team of one of the best Georgian agencies;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • participation in large and unusual projects;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • decent pay.
              .vacancies__request
                a.btn(href="#" js-open-request) SEND REQUEST
